UNITED STATES DISTRICT COURT SOUTHERN DISTRICT OF NEW YORK
United States of America,
-v-
Ghislain Maxwell,
Defendant.
ALISON J. NATHAN, District Judge:
Juror Number 70 is directed to submit the receipts associated with the transportation cost incurred on Wednesday 8, 2021, to the Jury Administrator.
Upon receipt, the Clerk of Court is directed to reimburse Juror Number 70 for said cost.
SO ORDERED.
Dated: December 8, 2021 New York, New York
ALISON J. NATHAN United States District Judge
